# Landing Page Development Patterns

This project specializes in Korean investment advice landing pages with BAND integration.

## Common Landing Page Sections

### Hero Section
- Modern hero design with grid layout
- Expert card with stats and testimonials
- Call-to-action buttons (BAND integration)
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach

### Success Cases (실적)
- Performance tables showing investment returns
- Animation effects for highlighting gains
- Structured data presentation

### Benefits (메리트)
- Why choose this service explanations
- Image + text combinations
- Trust-building content

### Testimonials (후기)
- User success stories with photos
- Age/occupation demographic info
- Detailed user experiences

### FAQ Section
- Collapsible Q&A format
- jQuery-powered interactions
- Common questions about the service

