## Styling Conventions

### Color Scheme
- Primary: `#007bff` (blue variations)
- Success: `#1ccc21` (BAND green)
- Accent: `#ff6b9d` (pink for highlights)

### Typography
- Korean text: `'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif`
- System fonts: `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI'`

### Responsive Breakpoints
- Desktop: Default styles
- Tablet: `@media screen and (max-width: 1024px)`
- Mobile: `@media screen and (max-width: 768px)`
- Small Mobile: `@media screen and (max-width: 480px)`

## Animation Patterns

### Button Animations
```css
@keyframes switch {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale3d(1, 1, 1); }
  50% { transform: scale3d(0.9, 0.9, 0.9); }
}
```

### Glow Effects
```css
@keyframes bandGlow {
  0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 200, 81, 0.25); }
  50% { box-shadow: 0 6px 25px rgba(0, 200, 81, 0.35); }
}
```

## Content Structure

### Korean Text Patterns
- Friendly, conversational tone
- Direct addressing ("너", "우리")
- Emphasis on trust and results
- Clear benefit statements

### Call-to-Action Hierarchy
1. Primary: BAND friend addition
2. Secondary: Information requests
3. Tertiary: FAQ engagement
